race.description: Family Of League / Armidale Rugby League Hcp
race.comment: DESERT COUGAR (2) ran below expectations last time at Inverell, finishing fifth and beaten 2.75 lengths starting at $2.80. Going up a level this time but she has the ability to mix it with them. CRYPTIC VERSE (7) did little when ninth over 1400m at Inverell last start, a less impressive effort than her eighth at Tamworth the run before. A win is not out of the question from the low gate. MUTINY (5) recorded a strong maiden win over 1050m at Inverell last time, getting there by 2 lengths. Sparingly raced and has more to offer. Looks well placed and she is definitely worth including. GERETY (1) is experiencing a long win drought, extended last start when seventh over 1100m at this track after being in contention on the bend. Big drop in grade.
